    {
      "id": "26.10-definitions",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.10",
      "text": "where\nKz = Velocity pressure exposure coefficient, see Section 26.10.1;\nKzt = Topographic factor, see Section 26.8.2;\nKd = Ground elevation factor, see Section 26.9;\nV = Basic wind speed, see Section 26.5; and\nqz = Velocity pressure at height z.",
