    {
      "id": "26.10-basic-wind-speed",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.10",
      "text": "The basic wind speed, V, used in determination of design wind loads on rooftop structures, rooftop equipment, and other building appurtenances shall consider the Risk Category equal to the greater of the following:",
